WhatsApp is a great app and I use it daily, but the new @all tag feature in groups is quite disturbing. Even though only admins can use it, it generates unnecessary notifications for everyone, especially in large groups. Many admins use it too frequently for non-urgent messages. Please consider adding an option to disable @all notifications or limit its usage. More control over mentions would greatly improve the user experience. Overall, still a very useful app.
